ss=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蘇聯死左之後咪到小支支，之後越南<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:12:45.000Z","msg":"越南醒目仔嚟<br />\n一早已經玩革新開放政策<br />\n好早期已經有得俾你玩全國直選（依然係共黨嘅人）<br />\n俾你玩youtube facebook 同西方接軌<br />\n開放黨內民主 國會直播<br />\n間唔中有啲唔同派系嘅會撳下反對掣 批評下啲官咁<br />\n等大家覺得黨內民主work喎咁<br />\n去分散民怨"},{"pid":"526983e3f5a5dfb3ef7db60942d38ff0426b1d7d","tid":1189900,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe14286adbc111df1a5fc28ec341d7d5c18f1a4b","tid":1189900,"uid":53632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:37:33.000Z","msg":"妄議大政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國人就應該跟著黨走，聽黨指揮，没有習大大，你們什麼也不是"}]}